003package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
004
005import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.util.IVersionInfo;
006
007/**
008 * Provides version information for the underlying Metaschema implementation used by this library.
009 */
010public class MetaschemaVersion implements IVersionInfo {
011
012  private static final String NAME = "metaschema";
013  private static final String BUILD_VERSION = "2.1.0";
014  private static final String BUILD_TIMESTAMP = "2024-11-26T16:21:36+0000";
015  private static final String COMMIT = "b6601f7";
016  private static final String BRANCH = "b6601f7430f83f1a53a11bf32575b69e131bc912";
017  private static final String CLOSEST_TAG = "";
018  private static final String ORIGIN = "https://github.com/metaschema-framework/metaschema.git";
019
020  @Override
021  public String getName() {
022    return NAME;
023  }
024
025  @Override
026  public String getVersion() {
027    return BUILD_VERSION;
028  }
029
030  @Override
031  public String getBuildTimestamp() {
032    return BUILD_TIMESTAMP;
033  }
034
035  @Override
036  public String getGitOriginUrl() {
037    return ORIGIN;
038  }
039
040  @Override
041  public String getGitCommit() {
042    return COMMIT;
043  }
044
045  @Override
046  public String getGitBranch() {
047    return BRANCH;
048  }
049
050  @Override
051  public String getGitClosestTag() {
052    return CLOSEST_TAG;
053  }
054}
